Create a method for the Remote API which allows diffs to be generated. Since this functionality is already in Confluence, it shouldn't be too difficult to implement.

This would be useful for keeping translations up-to-date. We know the date of the original translation, and wish to generate a diff of all changes to the page between that date and the current version of the page. This needs to be accessible via the remote API in order for it to be easily automated.

