Currently, the Calendar macro only allows you to paste a link into the "link" box.  Many times, I want to link back to a page within my Wiki, but should the name or location of the page change, the link would be broken.

If there is a way to use the wiki markup when entering a new event, it would allow the user to reference more than one page in the event and have an internal link that continues to update as the name and location changes.

